[{"Id": 1013615, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "He was born in 1 AH. He hosted Muslim ibn Aqil in Kufa but was imprisoned in the dungeons of Ubaydullah ibn Ziyaad during the massacre at Karbala. After his release he launched a campaign under the leadership of Ibrahim ibn Malik’e Ashtar to avenge the martyrdom of Imam Husain (a.s). During his uprising many involved in the martyrdom of Imam Husain (a.s) and his family, were pursued and killed including Shimr ibn Zil Jawshan, Khowli ibn Yazid, Umar ibn Saad and Ubaydullah ibn Ziyaad. After 18 months of rule in Kufa, Mukhtar was killed by Musab ibn Zubair in 67 AH. Recite his ziyarat in the following way…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Janabe Mukhtar 1 hijri mein paiyda huwe. Unho ne Janabe Muslim ki madad ki magar Waqeya Karbala ke waqt woh Ubaydullah ibne Ziyaad ke qaid khaane mein thay. Jab qaid se rehaah huwe to unho ne Ibrahim Ibne Malik’e Ashtar ke saath Imam Husain (a) aur unke ghar waalo’n ke qaatilo’n se intekaam liya jis mein Shimr ibne Zil Jawshan, Khowli ibne Yazid, Umar ibne Saad aur Ubaydullah ibne Ziyaad bhi shaamil hai. Takreeban 18 mahine Kufa mein hukumat ki aur 67 hijri mein Musab ibne Zubair ke haatho shaheed huwe. Unki ziyarat is tarah se padhe…", "UrduDescription": null, "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null,